            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# CleanSweep 1.0.1

## What's New

- Added optional in-app updates powered by Sparkle 2. Automatic update checks
  and automatic downloads stay off until you enable them in Settings; no system
  information is ever uploaded.
- Refined layouts for macOS 27, including toolbar and sidebar alignment.
- Fixed list scrolling misalignment while resizing the window.
- Background item scanning now runs only when explicitly requested.

## 更新内容

- 新增基于 Sparkle 2 的应用内更新(可选)。自动检查与自动下载默认关闭,
  仅在设置中主动开启后生效;不会上传任何系统信息。
- 优化 macOS 27 下的界面布局,包括工具栏与侧边栏对齐。
- 修复窗口缩放时列表滚动错位的问题。
- 后台项目扫描现在仅在明确请求时执行。
]]></description>
